overview: One of pro wrestling’s most outspoken and controversial figures takes the YouShoot oath to answer EVERYTHING you ask! This classic, from 2008, was one of the wildest, most out of control shoots the business has ever seen.  Jamie Dundee brings out the hottest topics in the public and he does not back down one bit as he swings back at viewers, wrestlers, and just about anyone in the way!  Join Kayfabe Commentaries in their revolutionary shoot-style interview series…YouShoot. The only series for the people, of the people, and BY the people!
title: YouShoot: Jamie  Dundee
